---

<section
    class="min-h-screen flex flex-col items-center justify-center relative py-32 bg-[#000000] text-[#22c55e] overflow-hidden font-mono"
>
    
    <div class="absolute inset-0 pointer-events-none opacity-20 overflow-hidden">
        {
            Array.from({ length: 20 }).map((_, i) => (
                <div
                    class="absolute text-xs animate-matrix-rain"
                    style={`left: ${i * 5}%; animation-duration: ${Math.random() * 2 + 2}s; animation-delay: ${Math.random() * 2}s;`}
                >
                    101101001
                </div>
            ))
        }
    </div>

    <div class="container mx-auto px-6 max-w-4xl relative z-10">
        <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row-reverse gap-16 items-center">
            <div class="w-full md:w-1/2 space-y-8">
                <span
                    class="text-[#4ade80] text-xs tracking-widest uppercase border-b border-[#15803d] pb-2"
                    >La Medida de la Sorpresa</span
                >
                <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl italic text-white font-serif">El Bit</h2>

                <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed text-[#bbf7d0]/90 font-sans">
                    ¿Cómo mides la información? ¿Cómo pesas una conversación telefónica o una
                    imagen? Claude Shannon se dio cuenta de que la información es la resolución de
                    la incertidumbre.
                </p>

                <div
                    class="bg-[#14532d]/30 p-6 rounded-sm border border-[#22c55e]/50 mt-4 backdrop-blur-sm"
                >
                    <h3 class="text-[#86efac] font-bold mb-2">Cara o Cruz</h3>
                    <p class="text-sm text-[#dcfce7] leading-relaxed font-sans">
                        La unidad mínima es la respuesta a una pregunta de Sí/No con 50% de
                        probabilidad. Eso es 1 Bit.
                    </p>
                    <p class="mt-4 text-sm text-[#4ade80]">
                        Todo lo digital, desde este texto hasta el video más complejo, es solo una
                        montaña masiva de monedas lanzadas al aire.
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="w-full md:w-1/2 flex justify-center relative h-[400px]">
                
                <div class="relative w-full h-full flex items-center justify-center">
                    <svg viewBox="0 0 300 300" class="w-full h-full overflow-visible">
                        
                        <g transform="translate(150, 150)">
                            <circle
                                cx="0"
                                cy="0"
                                r="50"
                                fill="#14532d"
                                stroke="#22c55e"
                                stroke-width="2"
                                class="animate-coin-flip"></circle>

                            
                            <text
                                x="0"
                                y="15"
                                text-anchor="middle"
                                fill="#22c55e"
                                font-size="40"
                                font-weight="bold"
                                class="animate-text-1">1</text
                            >
                            
                            <text
                                x="0"
                                y="15"
                                text-anchor="middle"
                                fill="#22c55e"
                                font-size="40"
                                font-weight="bold"
                                class="animate-text-0"
                                opacity="0">0</text
                            >
                        </g>

                        
                        <g opacity="0.3" stroke="#22c55e" stroke-width="1">
                            <line x1="150" y1="210" x2="100" y2="260"></line>
                            <line x1="150" y1="210" x2="200" y2="260"></line>
                            <circle cx="100" cy="260" r="5" fill="#22c55e"></circle>
                            <circle cx="200" cy="260" r="5" fill="none"></circle>
                        </g>
                    </svg>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

<style>
    @keyframes matrixRain {
        from {
            transform: translateY(-100%);
        }
        to {
            transform: translateY(100vh);
        }
    }
    .animate-matrix-rain {
        writing-mode: vertical-rl;
        animation-timing-function: linear;
        animation-iteration-count: infinite;
    }

    @keyframes coinFlip {
        0% {
            transform: scaleY(1);
        }
        50% {
            transform: scaleY(0);
        } 
        100% {
            transform: scaleY(1);
        }
    }
    .animate-coin-flip {
        animation: coinFlip 2s ease-in-out infinite;
    }

    @keyframes showOne {
        0%,
        49% {
            opacity: 1;
        }
        50%,
        100% {
            opacity: 0;
        }
    }
    .animate-text-1 {
        animation: showOne 2s step-end infinite;
    }

    @keyframes showZero {
        0%,
        49% {
            opacity: 0;
        }
        50%,
        100% {
            opacity: 1;
        }
    }
    .animate-text-0 {
        animation: showZero 2s step-end infinite;
    }
</style>
